WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:11.495 --> 00:00:12.961
[Insect buzzing]

2
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:20.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

3
00:00:28.628 --> 00:00:29.828
YEP.

4
00:00:31.264 --> 00:00:32.363
YEP.

5
00:00:34.234 --> 00:00:35.333
YEP.

6
00:00:36.103 --> 00:00:37.368
MMM-HMM.

7
00:00:38.105 --> 00:00:39.220
[Slurps]

8
00:00:39.289 --> 00:00:41.340
YOU KNOW WHAT IT COULD BE?

9
00:00:41.408 --> 00:00:43.408
THAT DAMN STARTER MOTOR.

10
00:00:43.477 --> 00:00:45.437
YOU GETTING GOOD COMPRESSION?

11
00:00:45.662 --> 00:00:46.778
YEAH.

12
00:00:47.681 --> 00:00:49.642
I KNOW WHAT'S WRONG WITH IT.

13
00:00:49.666 --> 00:00:51.366
IT'S A FORD.

14
00:00:51.435 --> 00:00:54.068
YOU KNOW WHAT THEY SAY
FORD STANDS FOR. DON'T YOU?

15
00:00:54.138 --> 00:00:56.338
IT STANDS FOR
"FIX IT AGAIN. TONY."

16
00:00:56.406 --> 00:00:57.406
[Laughs]

17
00:00:57.474 --> 00:00:59.808
YOU'RE THINKING OF A FIAT. DALE.

18
00:01:00.494 --> 00:01:03.362
"FIX IT AGAIN"...

19
00:01:06.267 --> 00:01:07.799
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT YOU DO.

20
00:01:07.868 --> 00:01:10.563
YOU JUST TAKE THEM DAMN SPARK
PLUGS OUT. AND IN THAT LITTLE HOLE.

21
00:01:10.587 --> 00:01:13.399
YOU JUST PUT A LITTLE OIL ROUND
THERE. JUST LIKE BOBBY UNSER SAID.

22
00:01:13.423 --> 00:01:15.607
"THE SHOCK'D GO
BOO-BOOM." JUST LIKE THAT.

23
00:01:17.060 --> 00:01:20.028
WELL. I WISH IT WERE
THAT SIMPLE. BOOMHAUER.

24
00:01:20.114 --> 00:01:22.898
BUT I'LL TELL YOU WHAT
MY TRUCK REALLY NEEDS.

25
00:01:22.966 --> 00:01:24.383
LEADERSHIP.

26
00:01:24.451 --> 00:01:26.835
DETROIT HASN'T
FELT ANY REAL PRIDE

27
00:01:26.904 --> 00:01:29.171
SINCE GEORGE BUSH WENT TO JAPAN

28
00:01:29.239 --> 00:01:32.073
AND VOMITED ON
THEIR AUTO EXECUTIVES.

29
00:01:32.142 --> 00:01:33.558
WHO'S READY?

30
00:01:34.861 --> 00:01:36.461
[Birds chirping]

31
00:01:36.530 --> 00:01:38.696
[Ice rustling]

32
00:01:38.765 --> 00:01:41.311
YOU ALL CATCH THE
<i>SEINFELD</i> SHOW LAST NIGHT?

33
00:01:41.335 --> 00:01:42.234
YEP.

34
00:01:42.303 --> 00:01:43.579
OH. HELL. I MISSED IT.

35
00:01:43.603 --> 00:01:44.887
I TELL YOU WHAT.

36
00:01:44.972 --> 00:01:47.083
YOU SEE THAT PART WHERE
DANG OLD GEORGE COME IN THERE?

37
00:01:47.107 --> 00:01:49.019
HE'S TALKING ABOUT
TASTING HIS OWN BURP.

38
00:01:49.043 --> 00:01:50.409
AND KRAMER COMES SLIDING IN

39
00:01:50.477 --> 00:01:52.138
[Laughing] JUST LIKE
HE ALWAYS DOES.

40
00:01:52.162 --> 00:01:53.562
I TELL YOU WHAT. MAN.

41
00:01:53.631 --> 00:01:56.214
THEM DANG OLD NEW
YORK BOYS. HA-HA.

42
00:01:56.283 --> 00:01:58.166
JUST A SHOW ABOUT NOTHING.

43
00:01:58.235 --> 00:02:00.486
♪ [Theme music playing]

44
00:02:32.235 --> 00:02:34.219
WHAT YOU LISTENING TO. SON?

45
00:02:34.288 --> 00:02:35.737
I DON'T THINK YOU'D LIKE IT.

46
00:02:35.806 --> 00:02:36.850
WELL. WHY NOT?

47
00:02:36.874 --> 00:02:39.491
I LIKE THIS NEW
GENERATION OF MUSIC.

48
00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:41.576
[Phone ringing]

49
00:02:41.645 --> 00:02:42.577
[Woman] <i>HELLO?</i>

50
00:02:42.646 --> 00:02:43.995
[Farting sound]

51
00:02:44.064 --> 00:02:47.032
MOTHER OF GOD! IT'S
ALL TOILET SOUNDS!

52
00:02:47.100 --> 00:02:48.561
WHERE DID YOU RECORD THIS?

53
00:02:48.585 --> 00:02:50.068
I BOUGHT IT AT THE MALL.

54
00:02:50.137 --> 00:02:51.837
IT'S THE FUNNY PHONE JERKS.

55
00:02:51.906 --> 00:02:53.316
LET ME TELL YOU. BOBBY.

56
00:02:53.340 --> 00:02:55.924
THERE'S NOTHING FUNNY
ABOUT THESE SOUNDS.

57
00:02:55.993 --> 00:02:58.193
WHAT THAT PERSON
ON YOUR TAPE HAS

58
00:02:58.261 --> 00:03:00.145
IS A MEDICAL DISORDER.

59
00:03:00.214 --> 00:03:02.614
NOW YOU GET READY
FOR THE GAME. OK?

60
00:03:03.851 --> 00:03:05.800
AIN'T RIGHT.

61
00:03:06.904 --> 00:03:08.119
[Screams]

62
00:03:08.188 --> 00:03:09.199
OH. GOD!

63
00:03:09.223 --> 00:03:11.267
LUANNE. I THOUGHT YOU WENT HOME!

64
00:03:11.291 --> 00:03:13.941
NUH-UH. UNCLE HANK. MAMA
AND DADDY ARE STILL FIGHTING.

65
00:03:14.010 --> 00:03:15.955
WELL. YOU'RE WELCOME TO STAY.

66
00:03:15.979 --> 00:03:18.713
BUT FOR GOD'S SAKES.
GIRL. LOCK THE DOOR.

67
00:03:18.782 --> 00:03:21.699
I'VE GOT A MINOR SON
LIVING IN THIS HOUSE.

68
00:03:21.768 --> 00:03:24.018
[Car door opening]

69
00:03:24.087 --> 00:03:27.656
SO ARE YOU READY TO KICK
SOME WILDCAT BUTT. BOBBY?

70
00:03:28.091 --> 00:03:29.257
OK.

71
00:03:29.326 --> 00:03:30.992
NOW DON'T YOU WORRY. SON.

72
00:03:31.061 --> 00:03:32.627
YOU JUST DO YOUR BEST.

73
00:03:32.696 --> 00:03:34.407
DON'T LISTEN TO HER. BOBBY.

74
00:03:34.431 --> 00:03:35.809
IF YOU WANT TO WIN.

75
00:03:35.833 --> 00:03:38.461
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
DO BETTER THAN YOUR BEST.

76
00:03:38.485 --> 00:03:40.101
HOW DO I DO THAT?

77
00:03:40.170 --> 00:03:43.488
YOU GOTTA GIVE 110 PERCENT.

78
00:03:43.557 --> 00:03:45.802
THAT'S WHAT'LL GIVE
YOU THAT WINNING EDGE.

79
00:03:45.826 --> 00:03:49.561
BUT WHAT IF THE WILDCATS
GIVE 110 PERCENT. TOO?

80
00:03:49.630 --> 00:03:51.741
WELL. THEN YOU GOTTA
TRY EVEN HARDER.

81
00:03:51.765 --> 00:03:54.332
HOW ABOUT IF BOBBY
GAVE 112 PERCENT?

82
00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:56.467
UH. SURE. THAT'D WORK.

83
00:03:56.536 --> 00:03:59.570
OR MAYBE 113.

84
00:03:59.639 --> 00:04:00.571
[Sighs]

85
00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:02.651
YEAH. YEAH. THAT'S EVEN BETTER.

86
00:04:02.675 --> 00:04:04.192
MMM. NO. UH-UH. I DON'T KNOW.

87
00:04:04.260 --> 00:04:06.127
13 IS A VERY UNLUCKY NUMBER.

88
00:04:06.196 --> 00:04:08.496
LOOK. WE'RE NOT
TALKING ABOUT 13.

89
00:04:08.565 --> 00:04:11.115
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT 113.

90
00:04:11.184 --> 00:04:12.617
AND EVEN...

91
00:04:12.686 --> 00:04:15.720
OK. GIVE 112. WHAT'S
THE DIFFERENCE?

92
00:04:15.789 --> 00:04:19.157
LOOK. BOBBY. JUST
DO YOUR BEST. OK?

93
00:04:19.209 --> 00:04:20.374
[Crowd chattering]

94
00:04:22.045 --> 00:04:24.429
SWING. BOBBY! SWING! SWING!

95
00:04:24.497 --> 00:04:26.197
[Muttering]

96
00:04:26.266 --> 00:04:27.165
BALL ONE.

97
00:04:27.234 --> 00:04:28.874
GOOD EYE. HONEY. GOOD EYE.

98
00:04:30.220 --> 00:04:32.054
OH. FOR CRYING OUT LOUD.

99
00:04:33.874 --> 00:04:37.192
BOBBY. YOU CAN'T MAKE AN
OMELET WITHOUT BREAKING EGGS.

100
00:04:37.260 --> 00:04:38.693
AND YOU CAN'T GET ON BASE

101
00:04:38.762 --> 00:04:40.428
WITHOUT TAKING A SWING.

102
00:04:40.496 --> 00:04:43.231
THE PITCHER COULD
WALK ME. COULDN'T HE?

103
00:04:43.300 --> 00:04:45.417
DON'T PLAY LAWYER-BALL. SON.

104
00:04:45.486 --> 00:04:47.585
NOW YOU HIT THE NEXT
ONE OUT OF THE PARK.

105
00:04:51.108 --> 00:04:52.907
RUN!

106
00:04:52.976 --> 00:04:55.126
[Hank] RUN! RUN!

107
00:04:55.195 --> 00:04:56.210
WHEW!

108
00:04:56.279 --> 00:04:57.579
[Whistling]

109
00:04:58.916 --> 00:05:00.876
LOOK AT THE BATTER. BOY!

110
00:05:00.900 --> 00:05:02.134
WATCH THE BALL!

111
00:05:02.202 --> 00:05:03.151
HUH?

112
00:05:03.219 --> 00:05:04.402
WHAT?

113
00:05:04.471 --> 00:05:06.298
HEY. DON'T LOOK AT ME!

114
00:05:06.322 --> 00:05:07.867
KEEP YOUR EYE ON THE BALL.

115
00:05:07.891 --> 00:05:09.824
KEEP MY EYE ON THE WHAT?

116
00:05:09.893 --> 00:05:11.387
STOP LOOKING AT ME. BOY!

117
00:05:11.411 --> 00:05:12.611
WATCH THE BALL!

118
00:05:12.679 --> 00:05:14.763
CAN'T HEAR YOU. DAD!

119
00:05:14.831 --> 00:05:16.330
[Crowd gasps]

120
00:05:17.417 --> 00:05:18.332
[Sighs]

121
00:05:18.401 --> 00:05:19.495
DON'T WORRY. BOBBY.

122
00:05:19.519 --> 00:05:21.347
YOU PLAYED A GOOD GAME.

123
00:05:21.371 --> 00:05:23.600
[Hank] I GOTTA STOP
IN HERE FOR A MINUTE.

124
00:05:23.624 --> 00:05:26.825
AND GET ME SOME
WD-40 AND A TAP AND DIE.

125
00:05:26.894 --> 00:05:28.510
♪ [Muzak playing]

126
00:05:30.514 --> 00:05:33.681
[Woman] <i>MANAGER TO
REGISTER 47. PLEASE.</i>

127
00:05:33.751 --> 00:05:34.783
[Sighs]

128
00:05:34.852 --> 00:05:36.718
I HATE THIS PLACE.

129
00:05:36.787 --> 00:05:39.532
EXCUSE ME. WHERE IS THE
HARDWARE DEPARTMENT?

130
00:05:39.556 --> 00:05:42.568
WHERE IS THE
HARDWARE DEPARTMENT?

131
00:05:42.592 --> 00:05:43.825
UM. HMM.

132
00:05:43.894 --> 00:05:45.888
WHAT EXACTLY IS IT
YOU'RE LOOKING FOR?

133
00:05:45.912 --> 00:05:47.445
THE HARDWARE DEPARTMENT.

134
00:05:47.514 --> 00:05:50.393
YEAH. BUT ARE YOU LOOKING
FOR. LIKE. A TOOL OR SOMETHING?

135
00:05:50.417 --> 00:05:52.083
WHAT DIFFERENCE DOES IT MAKE?

136
00:05:52.152 --> 00:05:52.967
HUH.

137
00:05:53.036 --> 00:05:54.547
WHAT DIFFERENCE DOES IT MAKE?

138
00:05:54.571 --> 00:05:55.820
[Sighs]

139
00:05:55.889 --> 00:05:59.174
OK. I'M LOOKING FOR A TAP
AND DIE AND SOME WD-40.

140
00:05:59.242 --> 00:06:01.743
HUH. WELL. WHAT IS IT
THAT YOU'RE TRYING TO DO?

141
00:06:01.812 --> 00:06:05.980
I'M TRYING TO BUY A TAP
AND DIE AND SOME WD-40

142
00:06:06.049 --> 00:06:08.533
AND GET OUT OF THIS
GODFORSAKEN STORE!

143
00:06:08.602 --> 00:06:09.534
OH.

144
00:06:09.603 --> 00:06:11.180
A-AND WHAT IS A TAP AND DIE?

145
00:06:11.204 --> 00:06:12.687
OK! FORGET IT!

146
00:06:12.756 --> 00:06:14.450
LET'S SAY I WANT A HAMMER!

147
00:06:14.474 --> 00:06:16.257
DO YOU KNOW WHAT A HAMMER IS?

148
00:06:16.326 --> 00:06:18.493
THAT'S WHAT I WANT!
A DAMNED HAMMER!

149
00:06:18.579 --> 00:06:20.895
NOW WHERE IN THE
HELL WOULD I GO?

150
00:06:20.964 --> 00:06:22.442
HEY. THAT'S THAT HANK HILL FELLA

151
00:06:22.466 --> 00:06:24.160
THAT LIVES ON THE
BLOCK NEXT TO US.

152
00:06:24.184 --> 00:06:25.595
HE SURE HAS A
TEMPER. DOESN'T HE?

153
00:06:25.619 --> 00:06:26.952
SURE DOES.

154
00:06:27.020 --> 00:06:29.782
MAKES YOU WONDER WHO
GAVE HIS BOY THAT BLACK EYE.

155
00:06:29.806 --> 00:06:32.591
UH. YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE
TO PAY FOR THAT. DUDE.

156
00:06:32.643 --> 00:06:33.820
YOU'RE FIRED!

157
00:06:33.844 --> 00:06:34.844
HMM.

158
00:06:34.911 --> 00:06:36.794
ELLA SAYS SHE SAW
HANK HIT HIS SON.

159
00:06:36.863 --> 00:06:40.159
REALLY? I HEARD HE THREATENED A
CLERK IN MEGA LO MART WITH A HAMMER.

160
00:06:40.183 --> 00:06:41.911
DID YOU HEAR ABOUT HANK HILL?

161
00:06:41.935 --> 00:06:43.301
HE BEAT UP HIS SON.

162
00:06:43.370 --> 00:06:45.448
AND THEN SOME LADIES IN
MEGA LO MART TRIED TO STOP HIM.

163
00:06:45.472 --> 00:06:47.083
AND HE BEAT THEM UP. TOO.

164
00:06:47.107 --> 00:06:49.667
WELL. SOMEBODY REALLY OUGHT
TO REPORT HIM FOR THE BOY'S SAKE.

165
00:06:49.726 --> 00:06:52.376
[Anthony] <i>YOU SAY HE
HIT HIS SON WITH A BAT?</i>

166
00:06:52.445 --> 00:06:55.080
NO. THAT IS DEFINITELY
NOT ACCEPTABLE.

167
00:06:55.148 --> 00:06:56.481
I WISH I COULD. MA'AM.

168
00:06:56.549 --> 00:06:57.849
BUT THE REGULATIONS SAY

169
00:06:57.918 --> 00:07:00.518
WE CAN'T TAKE CUSTODY OF
THE BOY WITHOUT AN INTERVIEW.

170
00:07:00.587 --> 00:07:02.420
DON'T YOU WORRY.
HE'S IN THE SYSTEM NOW.

171
00:07:02.489 --> 00:07:04.122
I AM ON MY WAY.

172
00:07:06.259 --> 00:07:08.293
[Whimpers]

173
00:07:08.361 --> 00:07:10.540
HEY. I KNOW WHAT'S
WRONG WITH YOUR TRUCK.

174
00:07:10.564 --> 00:07:13.047
IT'S YOUR QUOTE-UNQUOTE
"POLLUTION CONTROL."

175
00:07:13.116 --> 00:07:14.349
I HEARD ON TALK RADIO

176
00:07:14.417 --> 00:07:15.884
YOU DON'T EVEN NEED 'EM.

177
00:07:15.952 --> 00:07:18.035
THEY'RE JUST AN EGGHEAD
GOVERNMENT PLOT.

178
00:07:18.104 --> 00:07:21.789
HOW IS CUTTING DOWN ON
POLLUTION A GOVERNMENT PLOT. DALE?

179
00:07:21.858 --> 00:07:23.524
OPEN UP YOUR EYES. MAN.

180
00:07:23.593 --> 00:07:25.860
THEY'RE TRYING TO
CONTROL GLOBAL WARMING.

181
00:07:25.929 --> 00:07:26.845
GET IT?

182
00:07:26.913 --> 00:07:28.446
GLO-BAL.

183
00:07:28.514 --> 00:07:29.864
SO... WHAT?

184
00:07:29.950 --> 00:07:32.712
THAT'S CODE FOR U.N.
COMMISSARS TELLING AMERICANS

185
00:07:32.736 --> 00:07:35.464
WHAT TEMPERATURE IT'S
GONNA BE IN OUR OUTDOORS.

186
00:07:35.488 --> 00:07:37.121
I SAY LET THE WORLD WARM UP.

187
00:07:37.190 --> 00:07:40.425
SEE WHAT BOUTROS
BOUTROS-GHALI-GHALI THINKS ABOUT THAT.

188
00:07:40.493 --> 00:07:41.493
[Sniffs]

189
00:07:41.527 --> 00:07:43.528
WE'LL GROW ORANGES IN ALASKA.

190
00:07:43.580 --> 00:07:45.541
DALE. YOU GIBLET-HEAD.

191
00:07:45.565 --> 00:07:47.165
WE LIVE IN TEXAS.

192
00:07:47.233 --> 00:07:49.600
IT'S ALREADY 110 IN THE SUMMER.

193
00:07:49.669 --> 00:07:51.780
AND IF IT GETS ONE
DEGREE HOTTER.

194
00:07:51.804 --> 00:07:53.566
I'M GONNA KICK YOUR ASS.

195
00:07:53.590 --> 00:07:54.806
[Thumping]

196
00:07:54.875 --> 00:07:58.042
WHAT IN GOD'S NAME IS
THAT THUMPING SOUND?

197
00:07:58.111 --> 00:07:59.377
[Thumping]

198
00:07:59.445 --> 00:08:01.624
BOBBY. WHY DON'T YOU GO
OUT AND HELP YOUR DADDY?

199
00:08:01.648 --> 00:08:03.848
YOU HAVE BEEN WATCHING
WAY TOO MUCH T.V.. SON.

200
00:08:03.917 --> 00:08:04.783
UH?

201
00:08:04.851 --> 00:08:06.462
COME ON. COME ON. BOBBY. UP.

202
00:08:06.486 --> 00:08:08.369
NO MORE T.V. TURN IT OFF NOW.

203
00:08:08.438 --> 00:08:09.854
<i>[Crying]</i>

204
00:08:10.824 --> 00:08:11.824
OH.

205
00:08:11.858 --> 00:08:13.603
OH. GOD LOVE THAT POOR MAN.

206
00:08:13.627 --> 00:08:14.426
OH!

207
00:08:14.494 --> 00:08:15.494
[Shrieks]

208
00:08:16.446 --> 00:08:18.079
THERE. THAT'S BETTER.

209
00:08:21.918 --> 00:08:23.501
[Doorbell rings]

210
00:08:24.137 --> 00:08:26.404
[Thumping]

211
00:08:26.472 --> 00:08:28.718
HELLO. I'M A SOCIAL
WORKER WITH THE STATE.

212
00:08:28.742 --> 00:08:31.054
WOULD... WOULD YOU MIND IF
I TALK TO YOU FOR A MINUTE?

213
00:08:31.078 --> 00:08:33.361
WELL. SURE. COME ON IN.

214
00:08:33.429 --> 00:08:35.474
DAMN IT. THERE IT IS AGAIN.

215
00:08:35.498 --> 00:08:37.749
WHERE IS THAT
THUMPING COMING FROM?

216
00:08:37.817 --> 00:08:39.985
IT'S DRIVING ME CRAZY.

217
00:08:40.053 --> 00:08:42.231
COULD BE FAR-OFF HELICOPTERS.

218
00:08:42.255 --> 00:08:44.406
U.N. HELICOPTERS.

219
00:08:44.474 --> 00:08:45.952
DALE. WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

220
00:08:45.976 --> 00:08:48.944
GIVE ME SOME LIGHT!
NOW! I... I CAN'T SEE!

221
00:08:49.012 --> 00:08:50.778
OW! MY ARM!

222
00:08:50.864 --> 00:08:52.263
MY HEAD! OW!

223
00:08:52.331 --> 00:08:53.597
[Yelling]

224
00:08:53.666 --> 00:08:55.684
OW! GOD! GOD!

225
00:08:55.752 --> 00:08:56.835
MRS. HILL.

226
00:08:56.903 --> 00:08:59.048
WOULD YOU SAY YOUR
HUSBAND HAS A BAD TEMPER?

227
00:08:59.072 --> 00:09:00.171
WHO. HANK?

228
00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:02.823
NO. HANK IS AS GENTLE AS A LAMB.

229
00:09:03.643 --> 00:09:04.709
DANG.

230
00:09:04.777 --> 00:09:06.605
NO MORE BOUNCING THAT BALL!

231
00:09:06.629 --> 00:09:07.629
[Glass breaking]

232
00:09:07.664 --> 00:09:09.563
HANK. WE HAVE A VISITOR.

233
00:09:14.154 --> 00:09:15.914
SO YOUR ASSERTION. MR. HILL.

234
00:09:15.938 --> 00:09:18.734
IS THAT BOBBY GOT THE BLACK
EYE AT HIS BASEBALL GAME?

235
00:09:18.758 --> 00:09:20.686
THAT'S NOT MY ASSERTION.

236
00:09:20.710 --> 00:09:21.921
THAT'S WHAT HAPPENED.

237
00:09:21.945 --> 00:09:24.011
HAVE YOU EVER HIT
YOUR SON. MR. HILL?

238
00:09:24.097 --> 00:09:25.217
NO!

239
00:09:27.033 --> 00:09:29.295
WHAT THE HECK ARE YOU WRITING?

240
00:09:29.319 --> 00:09:31.853
ALL YOU GOTTA WRITE
IS ONE WORD. "NO"!

241
00:09:31.938 --> 00:09:33.188
MR. HILL.

242
00:09:33.256 --> 00:09:35.601
I FEEL THAT YOU'RE COMING
FROM AN ANGER MINDSET.

243
00:09:35.625 --> 00:09:37.892
AND IF YOU'RE PROJECTING
THIS ANGER ONTO ME.

244
00:09:37.961 --> 00:09:40.594
IT GIVES ME GRAVE CONCERNS
AS TO HOW YOU FACILITATE

245
00:09:40.663 --> 00:09:42.446
YOUR SON'S GROWTH IN PRIVATE.

246
00:09:42.515 --> 00:09:44.493
MISTER. I HAVE NOT BEGUN

247
00:09:44.517 --> 00:09:46.695
TO PROJECT MY ANGER ONTO YOU.

248
00:09:46.719 --> 00:09:47.819
MRS. HILL.

249
00:09:47.887 --> 00:09:49.699
HOW DID YOU GET THIS
HERE ON YOUR FOREHEAD?

250
00:09:49.723 --> 00:09:51.839
OH. THIS? WELL. BOBBY
THREW HIS BASEBALL AT ME.

251
00:09:51.908 --> 00:09:54.070
YOU THREW A BASEBALL
AT YOUR MOTHER?

252
00:09:54.094 --> 00:09:56.243
OH. HANK. IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

253
00:09:56.312 --> 00:09:58.223
SO WOULD THIS BE
THE SAME "BASEBALL"

254
00:09:58.247 --> 00:10:00.231
THAT GAVE BOBBY THE BLACK EYE?

255
00:10:02.819 --> 00:10:04.969
WITH HANK'S TRUCK
WHEN HE'S NOT AROUND?

256
00:10:05.038 --> 00:10:07.205
I'M GONNA HELP GET HIM
THIS ALTERNATOR OFF.

257
00:10:07.274 --> 00:10:08.274
[Snapping sound]

258
00:10:08.341 --> 00:10:09.341
UH. DALE.

259
00:10:09.409 --> 00:10:11.676
I THINK YOU RELEASED
THE BRAKE CABLE.

260
00:10:11.745 --> 00:10:12.745
DALE!

261
00:10:12.779 --> 00:10:14.162
NO. I DIDN'T.

262
00:10:16.032 --> 00:10:18.382
I GUESS I BETTER
GET GOING. UH...

263
00:10:18.451 --> 00:10:20.811
I GOT SOME EDGING TO DO.

264
00:10:22.839 --> 00:10:24.566
DO YOU WORK OUTSIDE
THE HOME. MRS. HILL?

265
00:10:24.590 --> 00:10:27.841
WELL. YES. I DO. I'M A
SUBSTITUTE SPANISH TEACHER.

266
00:10:27.910 --> 00:10:30.395
[Speaking Spanish]

267
00:10:30.463 --> 00:10:32.191
AND YOU JUST HAVE THE ONE SON?

268
00:10:32.215 --> 00:10:33.348
UH-HUH.

269
00:10:33.416 --> 00:10:35.450
YEAH. WELL. WE WOULD'VE
LIKED TO HAVE MORE KIDS.

270
00:10:35.518 --> 00:10:37.418
BUT HANK HAS A NARROW URETHRA.

271
00:10:37.487 --> 00:10:38.419
PEGGY!

272
00:10:38.488 --> 00:10:40.288
IN FACT. HANK'S SPERM COUNT...

273
00:10:40.357 --> 00:10:41.434
THAT'S ENOUGH.

274
00:10:41.458 --> 00:10:43.836
WHAT IN THE HELL DID
YOU TELL HIM THAT FOR?

275
00:10:43.860 --> 00:10:44.892
WELL. HE ASKED ME.

276
00:10:44.961 --> 00:10:47.106
HE ASKED YOU HOW
MANY KIDS WE HAVE.

277
00:10:47.130 --> 00:10:49.375
HE DIDN'T ASK YOU
ABOUT MY GLANDS.

278
00:10:49.399 --> 00:10:50.548
PLEASE. MR. HILL.

279
00:10:50.617 --> 00:10:52.650
LOUD IS NOT ALLOWED.

280
00:10:52.719 --> 00:10:53.801
WHAT THE...

281
00:10:53.869 --> 00:10:55.581
"LOUD IS NOT ALLOWED"?

282
00:10:55.605 --> 00:10:57.416
NOW YOU LISTEN TO ME. MISTER.

283
00:10:57.440 --> 00:11:00.291
I WORK FOR A LIVING.
AND I MEAN REAL WORK.

284
00:11:00.360 --> 00:11:02.543
NOT WRITING DOWN GOBBLEDYGOOK.

285
00:11:02.612 --> 00:11:05.279
I PROVIDE THE PEOPLE
OF THIS COMMUNITY

286
00:11:05.348 --> 00:11:08.599
WITH PROPANE AND
PROPANE ACCESSORIES.

287
00:11:08.668 --> 00:11:12.002
OH. WHEN I THINK OF ALL MY
HARD-EARNED TAX DOLLARS

288
00:11:12.071 --> 00:11:16.107
GOING TO PAY A BUNCH OF LITTLE
TWIG-BOY BUREAUCRATS LIKE YOU...

289
00:11:16.175 --> 00:11:18.643
IT JUST MAKES ME WANT TO...

290
00:11:18.712 --> 00:11:20.478
OH. OH. GOD. IT JUST...

291
00:11:21.263 --> 00:11:22.847
[Peggy] HANK?

292
00:11:22.915 --> 00:11:26.484
HONEY. BRING ME MY B.C. HEADACHE
POWDER AND A GLASS OF WATER.

293
00:11:26.553 --> 00:11:28.352
ALL RIGHT. HANK.

294
00:11:28.421 --> 00:11:31.299
NOW. YOU LISTEN HERE.
YOU SEE THAT BOY?

295
00:11:31.323 --> 00:11:32.690
THAT'S MY BOY.

296
00:11:32.759 --> 00:11:36.177
AND IF YOU EVER TRY TO TAKE
HIM AWAY. SO HELP ME GOD.

297
00:11:36.246 --> 00:11:39.731
I'LL TEAR YOU A NEW ONE
BIGGER THAN THE GRAND CANYON.

298
00:11:39.799 --> 00:11:42.416
NOW I WANT YOU TO
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE.

299
00:11:42.485 --> 00:11:43.935
YOU'RE NOT WELCOME HERE.

300
00:11:44.004 --> 00:11:47.955
I MEAN NOW. BEFORE I
GIVE YOU A BLACK EYE! GIT!

301
00:11:48.024 --> 00:11:50.925
<i>♪ [Battle Hymn Of
The Republic</i> playing]

302
00:11:50.994 --> 00:11:53.556
[Dale] <i>YOU WANT TO
KNOW ABOUT OL' HANK?</i>

303
00:11:53.580 --> 00:11:56.931
WELL. HANK'S GOT
A LOT OF PROBLEMS.

304
00:11:57.000 --> 00:12:00.118
HEY. BABY! HOW ABOUT
A COUPLE OF BEERS!

305
00:12:00.170 --> 00:12:01.552
SORRY. SUG'. GOTTA GO.

306
00:12:01.621 --> 00:12:04.283
I GOT ANOTHER MIGRAINE
TREATMENT WITH JOHN REDCORN.

307
00:12:04.307 --> 00:12:07.169
NANCY. YOU'VE BEEN GOING
TO THAT HEALER FOR 12 YEARS.

308
00:12:07.193 --> 00:12:09.594
AND YOU STILL GET
HEADACHES EVERY NIGHT.

309
00:12:09.662 --> 00:12:12.096
HEALING PROCESS
TAKES TIME. HONEY.

310
00:12:12.165 --> 00:12:14.126
♪ [Foreigner
performing <i>Hot Blooded]</i>

311
00:12:14.150 --> 00:12:16.395
[Social worker] <i>GETTING
BACK TO THE HILL FAMILY.</i>

312
00:12:16.419 --> 00:12:18.663
HAVE YOU EVER SEEN
HANK HIT HIS CHILD. BOBBY?

313
00:12:18.687 --> 00:12:20.054
HANK? NO SIR.

314
00:12:20.122 --> 00:12:22.256
BOBBY'S HIS PRIDE AND JOY...

315
00:12:22.325 --> 00:12:24.792
'CAUSE OF HIS NARROW URETHRA.

316
00:12:24.860 --> 00:12:25.900
[Snickers]

317
00:12:25.928 --> 00:12:27.339
ARE YOU ABSOLUTELY SURE?

318
00:12:27.363 --> 00:12:28.446
100 PERCENT.

319
00:12:28.514 --> 00:12:29.847
YOU CAN ASK MY SON.

320
00:12:29.916 --> 00:12:31.649
HE'S BOBBY'S BEST FRIEND.

321
00:12:31.717 --> 00:12:32.951
JOSEPH!

322
00:12:33.019 --> 00:12:34.569
WHAT IS IT. DADDY?

323
00:12:34.637 --> 00:12:36.370
YOU EVER SEEN HANK HIT BOBBY?

324
00:12:36.456 --> 00:12:37.938
NUH-UH. NEVER.

325
00:12:38.007 --> 00:12:39.607
SEE?

326
00:12:39.675 --> 00:12:41.475
NOW. YOU CAN JUST
MOVE ALONG NOW.

327
00:12:41.544 --> 00:12:44.222
I'VE BEEN CALLING Y'ALL PEOPLE
BETTER THAN A MONTH NOW.

328
00:12:44.246 --> 00:12:47.109
GRIPE ABOUT Y'ALL EVERY TIME THAT
DANG OL' DOG CROSSES THE STREET.

329
00:12:47.133 --> 00:12:50.195
STARTS YAPPING HIS JAW 24 HOURS
A DAY. AND NOBODY ANSWERED.

330
00:12:50.219 --> 00:12:52.130
HOW YOU SUPPOSED
TO DO ANYTHING ABOUT

331
00:12:52.154 --> 00:12:54.333
THAT DOG IF YOU JUST
GET ON YOUR COMPUTER?

332
00:12:54.357 --> 00:12:57.219
AIN'T GONNA COME OVER HERE
AND SHUT THAT DANG OL' DOG UP.

333
00:12:57.243 --> 00:12:59.604
[Bobby] AND THEN SOME
WEIRDO CAME OVER

334
00:12:59.628 --> 00:13:01.846
AND WAS ASKING US A
BUNCH OF QUESTIONS.

335
00:13:01.915 --> 00:13:03.130
YEAH.

336
00:13:03.199 --> 00:13:05.428
HE ASKED ME IF YOUR
DAD EVER WHUPPED YOU.

337
00:13:05.452 --> 00:13:06.611
HE HASN'T. RIGHT?

338
00:13:06.635 --> 00:13:07.701
OF COURSE NOT!

339
00:13:07.770 --> 00:13:10.471
YOU KNOW MY DAD. HE'S ALL BARK.

340
00:13:10.539 --> 00:13:12.640
BOY. THAT GUY GOT
HIM MAD. THOUGH.

341
00:13:12.709 --> 00:13:14.241
MY DAD WAS LIKE.

342
00:13:14.310 --> 00:13:16.394
[Imitating Hank] "GET
OUT OF MY HOUSE!

343
00:13:16.462 --> 00:13:19.530
"MY BOY AIN'T MUCH.
BUT HE'S ALL I GOT!"

344
00:13:20.199 --> 00:13:21.276
[Laughs]

345
00:13:21.300 --> 00:13:23.868
YOU DO GREAT IMPRESSIONS.

346
00:13:23.937 --> 00:13:25.302
LET ME TRY.

347
00:13:25.371 --> 00:13:28.172
"I'LL TEAR YOU A NEW ONE!

348
00:13:28.240 --> 00:13:30.724
"WHEN I GET MY HANDS ON YOU.

349
00:13:30.793 --> 00:13:32.921
"YOU LITTLE PEA-BRAIN.

350
00:13:32.945 --> 00:13:36.397
"I'LL BUST YOUR BUTT
INTO LITTLE PIECES!"

351
00:13:36.466 --> 00:13:37.998
OH. I KNEW IT!

352
00:13:38.985 --> 00:13:40.567
GOOD GOD. PEGGY.

353
00:13:40.636 --> 00:13:42.781
THIS WAS ON MY <i>ROAD & TRACK.</i>

354
00:13:42.805 --> 00:13:43.905
LUANNE!

355
00:13:43.973 --> 00:13:45.823
LUANNE. HONEY.
CAN WE TALK TO YOU?

356
00:13:45.891 --> 00:13:48.592
WAIT! WAIT! NOT WHILE I'M HERE.

357
00:13:48.661 --> 00:13:49.593
[Crying]

358
00:13:49.662 --> 00:13:50.989
MAMA'S IN JAIL.

359
00:13:51.013 --> 00:13:53.208
SHE WAS SAVING A QUART
OF BEER FOR BEFORE BED.

360
00:13:53.232 --> 00:13:55.744
AND DADDY THREW IT OUT. AND
SHE WENT AFTER HIM WITH A FORK.

361
00:13:55.768 --> 00:13:58.380
AND THE TRAILER TIPPED OVER.
AND EVERYTHING WENT UPSIDE DOWN.

362
00:13:58.404 --> 00:14:01.266
AND IT'S ALL GONNA BE ON <i>REAL
STORIES OF THE HIGHWAY PATROL!</i>

363
00:14:01.290 --> 00:14:05.159
AND THE WIG I STYLED FOR
BEAUTY ACADEMY IS RUINED.

364
00:14:06.195 --> 00:14:08.529
WHAT AM I GONNA DO. UNCLE HANK?

365
00:14:08.598 --> 00:14:09.763
UH. UH.

366
00:14:09.832 --> 00:14:11.098
THERE. THERE. UH.

367
00:14:11.167 --> 00:14:12.899
YOU CAN. UH. STAY WITH US

368
00:14:12.968 --> 00:14:15.202
TILL YOUR MAMA COMES HOME.

369
00:14:15.271 --> 00:14:17.338
AND YOU'LL. UH. STYLE A NEW WIG

370
00:14:17.406 --> 00:14:19.773
BETTER THAN BEFORE. UH...

371
00:14:19.842 --> 00:14:21.876
I'LL LET YOU USE MY TOOLS.

372
00:14:21.944 --> 00:14:22.877
OH.

373
00:14:22.945 --> 00:14:24.645
THANKS. UNCLE HANK.

374
00:14:26.232 --> 00:14:27.865
SHE HAS GOT TO GO.

375
00:14:27.933 --> 00:14:29.433
[Doorbell rings]

376
00:14:30.536 --> 00:14:31.485
BOBBY?

377
00:14:31.554 --> 00:14:33.015
BOBBY. ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

378
00:14:33.039 --> 00:14:33.971
COME ON OUT.

379
00:14:34.040 --> 00:14:35.840
I THOUGHT I TOLD
YOU TO GET LOST.

380
00:14:35.909 --> 00:14:37.274
COME ON. BOBBY.

381
00:14:37.343 --> 00:14:40.172
I CAN PUT YOU WITH A NICE
FOSTER FAMILY IN NORTH ARLEN.

382
00:14:40.196 --> 00:14:42.863
WHERE YOU CAN DEVELOP
HEALTHY LIFE ADAPTATIONS.

383
00:14:42.932 --> 00:14:44.281
AND THEY'VE GOT A POOL.

384
00:14:44.350 --> 00:14:46.145
HONEY. LET'S GIVE HIM LUANNE.

385
00:14:46.169 --> 00:14:49.002
HEY. I GOT A GIRL IN HERE
YOU CAN TAKE RIGHT NOW.

386
00:14:49.071 --> 00:14:51.806
DON'T YOU WANT TO LIVE
IN A HOUSE WITH A POOL?

387
00:14:51.874 --> 00:14:52.807
NO.

388
00:14:52.875 --> 00:14:54.158
SEE. TWIG BOY?

389
00:14:54.227 --> 00:14:56.761
NOW GET YOUR SKINNY
BUTT OFF OF MY PROPERTY.

390
00:14:56.830 --> 00:14:58.007
BOBBY.

391
00:14:58.031 --> 00:15:00.342
I KNOW YOU CAN'T
TALK IN FRONT OF HIM.

392
00:15:00.366 --> 00:15:02.700
I SAID GIT! GIT!
GET OUT OF HERE!

393
00:15:02.769 --> 00:15:03.717
OK.

394
00:15:03.786 --> 00:15:05.530
YOU ARE OUT OF CONTROL!

395
00:15:05.554 --> 00:15:07.754
YOU'RE OUT OF CONTROL. TWIGGY.

396
00:15:10.826 --> 00:15:12.242
[Slurping]

397
00:15:12.311 --> 00:15:14.256
MMM. THANKS FOR
THE LATTE. KENNETH.

398
00:15:14.280 --> 00:15:16.714
ANTHONY. COULD I
SEE YOU A MINUTE?

399
00:15:16.783 --> 00:15:18.783
SO ON THIS HILL FAMILY CASE.

400
00:15:18.851 --> 00:15:20.818
YOU COULDN'T CONFIRM
ANY ACTUAL ABUSE.

401
00:15:20.887 --> 00:15:22.330
BUT YOU STILL RECOMMENDED

402
00:15:22.354 --> 00:15:23.882
THE STATE TAKE CUSTODY?

403
00:15:23.906 --> 00:15:26.685
OH... OH. YEAH. I MEAN. THE WHOLE
NEIGHBORHOOD WAS REDNECK CITY.

404
00:15:26.709 --> 00:15:28.186
DID... DID YOU SEE IN THE REPORT

405
00:15:28.210 --> 00:15:29.488
HOW HE DENTED MY GEO?

406
00:15:29.512 --> 00:15:31.712
HMM. "REDNECK CITY."
THAT'S PRETTY FUNNY.

407
00:15:31.781 --> 00:15:33.080
WHERE YOU FROM. SON?

408
00:15:33.166 --> 00:15:34.315
LOS ANGELES.

409
00:15:34.383 --> 00:15:35.733
HMM.

410
00:15:35.801 --> 00:15:38.336
LET'S SEE HERE.
"HIT BY A BASEBALL."

411
00:15:38.388 --> 00:15:40.053
HMPH.

412
00:15:40.122 --> 00:15:42.490
SO. UH. HOW DID
YOU LIKE OL' HARVEY?

413
00:15:42.559 --> 00:15:43.636
[Gulps]

414
00:15:43.660 --> 00:15:44.803
WHO'S HARVEY?

415
00:15:44.827 --> 00:15:46.911
OH. HE'S THE LITTLE
LEAGUE COACH.

416
00:15:46.980 --> 00:15:50.197
YOU DID TALK TO THE LITTLE
LEAGUE COACH. DIDN'T YOU?

417
00:15:50.266 --> 00:15:51.476
[Gulps] HA. HA.

418
00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:52.800
[Drilling]

419
00:15:52.868 --> 00:15:54.151
[Banging]

420
00:15:55.238 --> 00:15:57.355
SON. HAVE YOU LOST YOUR MIND?

421
00:15:57.423 --> 00:15:59.473
DAD! WAIT! DAD.

422
00:15:59.541 --> 00:16:02.304
YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED
TO YELL AT ME ANYMORE.

423
00:16:02.328 --> 00:16:03.973
THE GUY FROM THE STATE

424
00:16:03.997 --> 00:16:09.033
SAID YOUR HOSTILITY INVALIDATES
OUR PARENT-CHILD CONTRACT.

425
00:16:09.101 --> 00:16:11.802
YOU'RE QUOTING
THAT TWIG BOY AT ME?

426
00:16:11.871 --> 00:16:13.353
HANK. THE NEIGHBORS.

427
00:16:13.422 --> 00:16:14.906
REMEMBER. HE SAID.

428
00:16:14.974 --> 00:16:16.819
"LOUD IS NOT ALLOWED." DAD...

429
00:16:16.843 --> 00:16:19.243
OR THEY'LL TAKE ME AWAY.

430
00:16:19.328 --> 00:16:20.560
[Sighs]

431
00:16:20.629 --> 00:16:21.778
OH. GOD.

432
00:16:23.382 --> 00:16:24.559
[Giggles]

433
00:16:24.583 --> 00:16:25.883
[Phone ringing]

434
00:16:26.452 --> 00:16:27.885
HELLO?

435
00:16:27.954 --> 00:16:30.432
[Boss] <i>IS THIS THE HILL
RESIDENCE? WHO AM I TALKING TO?</i>

436
00:16:30.456 --> 00:16:31.639
BOBBY HILL.

437
00:16:31.708 --> 00:16:34.308
<i>WELL. SON. THIS IS THE
STATE SOCIAL SERVICES.</i>

438
00:16:34.377 --> 00:16:37.010
<i>WE'RE CALLING OFF OUR
INVESTIGATION OF YOUR FATHER.</i>

439
00:16:37.079 --> 00:16:38.879
<i>THE WORKER THAT VISITED YOU</i>

440
00:16:38.948 --> 00:16:41.315
<i>WILL BE LEAVING THE OFFICE
AND GOING BACK TO L.A.</i>

441
00:16:41.384 --> 00:16:44.885
<i>NOW. YOU PLEASE TELL YOUR PARENTS
WE APOLOGIZE FOR THE MISUNDERSTANDING.</i>

442
00:16:44.953 --> 00:16:45.836
OK.

443
00:16:45.905 --> 00:16:47.271
I'LL TELL THEM. BYE.

444
00:16:47.340 --> 00:16:49.106
BOBBY. WHO WAS THAT?

445
00:16:49.175 --> 00:16:50.255
UH.

446
00:16:51.077 --> 00:16:52.476
WRONG NUMBER.

447
00:16:56.749 --> 00:16:58.249
♪ [Hank humming]

448
00:17:08.043 --> 00:17:10.589
[Luanne] I BORROWED YOUR
TRUCK THIS MORNING. UNCLE HANK.

449
00:17:10.613 --> 00:17:13.392
IT WOULDN'T START AT FIRST.
'CAUSE YOU HAD A CLOGGED FUEL LINE.

450
00:17:13.416 --> 00:17:15.736
BUT I BLEW IT CLEAN.

451
00:17:16.002 --> 00:17:17.002
HMM.

452
00:17:18.154 --> 00:17:19.052
HEY. BOBBY.

453
00:17:19.122 --> 00:17:21.038
GO PLUG THIS IN
THE GARAGE FOR ME.

454
00:17:26.829 --> 00:17:28.862
WANT TO SEE SOMETHING COOL?

455
00:17:32.618 --> 00:17:33.762
WHAT IN THE HECK?

456
00:17:33.786 --> 00:17:35.164
DON'T YOU SEE I'M WORKING HERE?

457
00:17:35.188 --> 00:17:36.903
CLOSE THE DANG DOOR.

458
00:17:36.972 --> 00:17:39.083
UH. BOB. JUST KEEP PUT... STOP!

459
00:17:39.107 --> 00:17:40.585
STOP HITTING THAT BUTTON!

460
00:17:40.609 --> 00:17:41.892
GIVE ME THAT THING!

461
00:17:41.961 --> 00:17:43.177
DAD.

462
00:17:43.245 --> 00:17:46.030
THAT'S NOT RESPECTFUL
ADULT-CHILD GROWTH DIALOGUE.

463
00:17:46.099 --> 00:17:47.948
I'LL GIVE YOU DIALOGUE

464
00:17:48.017 --> 00:17:51.402
THAT'S NOT COMING
FROM A CENTER OF ANGER.

465
00:17:51.470 --> 00:17:53.832
PLEASE RETURN THE GARAGE DOOR

466
00:17:53.856 --> 00:17:57.336
TO ITS FACTORY-PRESET
DOWN POSITION!

467
00:17:58.177 --> 00:17:59.237
[Chuckles]

468
00:17:59.261 --> 00:18:00.894
THAT IS COOL.

469
00:18:05.250 --> 00:18:07.851
[Hank] BOBBY. HEY!

470
00:18:07.920 --> 00:18:10.265
PLEASE. UH. RESPECT...

471
00:18:10.289 --> 00:18:13.889
MY FENCE'S RIGHT TO BE A FENCE.

472
00:18:14.293 --> 00:18:15.413
NOW!

473
00:18:17.063 --> 00:18:18.579
[Boys laughing]

474
00:18:19.765 --> 00:18:21.215
YOU CAN'T DO NOTHING.

475
00:18:21.283 --> 00:18:22.615
[Hank screaming]

476
00:18:22.684 --> 00:18:24.284
[Hank] HEY! HEY!

477
00:18:24.353 --> 00:18:26.169
YOU'RE ALL WET. DAD!

478
00:18:26.238 --> 00:18:27.738
[Hank howling]

479
00:18:29.858 --> 00:18:31.609
CREAK.

480
00:18:31.677 --> 00:18:33.010
[Imitating footsteps]

481
00:18:33.362 --> 00:18:34.411
BOING.

482
00:18:34.480 --> 00:18:35.979
WHAT ON GOD'S GREEN EARTH

483
00:18:36.048 --> 00:18:37.814
ARE YOU MAKING THOSE NOISES FOR?

484
00:18:37.883 --> 00:18:41.263
THEY'RE SOUND EFFECTS. LIKE
THAT GUY ON <i>POLICE ACADEMY.</i>

485
00:18:41.287 --> 00:18:43.965
THAT'S WHAT I'M GONNA DO
WHEN I GROW UP. I'VE DECIDED.

486
00:18:43.989 --> 00:18:46.257
AND DAD CAN'T SAY BOO ABOUT IT.

487
00:18:46.325 --> 00:18:47.658
BOBBY.

488
00:18:47.726 --> 00:18:50.244
A MAN FROM THE CHILD
PROTECTIVE SERVICES JUST CAME BY.

489
00:18:50.312 --> 00:18:52.896
NOW. HE SAID THAT HE
TOLD YOU LAST WEEK

490
00:18:52.965 --> 00:18:54.965
THAT THIS INVESTIGATION WAS OFF.

491
00:18:55.567 --> 00:18:56.583
OH.

492
00:18:57.286 --> 00:18:59.386
PLEASE DON'T TELL DAD!

493
00:18:59.472 --> 00:19:01.655
WELL. SON. I HAVE TO.
HE'S BEEN WORRIED.

494
00:19:01.724 --> 00:19:03.823
BUT I LIKE HIM BETTER THIS WAY.

495
00:19:03.892 --> 00:19:05.024
HOW COME?

496
00:19:05.093 --> 00:19:08.345
I CAN MAKE HIM LOVE ME
EVEN WHEN I SCREW UP.

497
00:19:08.413 --> 00:19:10.264
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK?

498
00:19:12.501 --> 00:19:13.578
[Sighs]

499
00:19:13.602 --> 00:19:15.568
IT'S HARD. PEGGY.

500
00:19:15.637 --> 00:19:19.157
I DON'T WANT TO LOSE MY
LITTLE BOY. MY ONLY SON.

501
00:19:19.708 --> 00:19:21.208
BUT. OH. IT'S HARD.

502
00:19:21.277 --> 00:19:22.809
WELL. YOU CAN RELAX.

503
00:19:22.878 --> 00:19:25.645
THE INVESTIGATION HAS
BEEN OFF FOR A WEEK.

504
00:19:25.714 --> 00:19:27.414
ONLY. BOBBY DIDN'T TELL US.

505
00:19:27.482 --> 00:19:28.482
I'LL KILL HIM!

506
00:19:28.550 --> 00:19:30.033
ALL RIGHT. CALM DOWN. HONEY.

507
00:19:30.102 --> 00:19:31.296
NOW LET ME EXPLAIN.

508
00:19:31.320 --> 00:19:32.797
HE DIDN'T DO IT TO BE MEAN.

509
00:19:32.821 --> 00:19:34.332
BOBBY HONESTLY DOESN'T THINK

510
00:19:34.356 --> 00:19:36.034
THAT YOU LOVE HIM ALL THE TIME.

511
00:19:36.058 --> 00:19:37.941
THAT'S CRAZY. COURSE I LOVE HIM.

512
00:19:38.010 --> 00:19:40.088
VERY GOOD. NOW. SAY IT TO BOBBY.

513
00:19:40.112 --> 00:19:41.578
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

514
00:19:41.630 --> 00:19:43.391
I WANT YOU TO TELL BOBBY

515
00:19:43.415 --> 00:19:45.727
THAT YOUR LOVE FOR
HIM IS UNCONDITIONAL.

516
00:19:45.751 --> 00:19:48.619
I CAN'T SAY THAT. I CAN'T!

517
00:19:48.687 --> 00:19:50.453
YOU KNOW HOW I WAS RAISED.

518
00:19:50.523 --> 00:19:52.206
WHAT MY FATHER'S LIKE.

519
00:19:52.275 --> 00:19:54.074
I GOT MY SHINS BLOWED OFF

520
00:19:54.143 --> 00:19:56.543
BY A JAPAN MAN'S MACHINE GUN!

521
00:19:56.612 --> 00:19:59.546
SO DON'T COME CRYING TO
ME WITH YOUR PROBLEMS!

522
00:20:00.799 --> 00:20:02.494
HONEY. I AM BEGGING YOU.

523
00:20:02.518 --> 00:20:04.029
FOR THE SAKE OF THIS FAMILY.

524
00:20:04.053 --> 00:20:05.363
YOU HAVE GOT TO DO IT.

525
00:20:05.387 --> 00:20:07.398
HE'S WAITING FOR YOU
OUT ON THE PORCH.

526
00:20:07.422 --> 00:20:08.822
OH. JEEZ.

527
00:20:08.891 --> 00:20:11.441
[Muttering] DAMN TWIG
BOY COMES OVER HERE...

528
00:20:12.895 --> 00:20:14.428
[Clears throat]

529
00:20:14.863 --> 00:20:16.023
UH...

530
00:20:16.532 --> 00:20:17.831
YOU. UH...

531
00:20:18.601 --> 00:20:20.901
YOU'RE MY SON.

532
00:20:20.969 --> 00:20:23.704
WELL. YOU KNOW.
WITH EVERYTHING. UH...

533
00:20:23.773 --> 00:20:25.406
THAT ENTAILS. UH...

534
00:20:26.175 --> 00:20:27.708
UH-HUH.

535
00:20:27.777 --> 00:20:28.858
UH.

536
00:20:30.296 --> 00:20:31.828
YOU KNOW. UH...

537
00:20:31.897 --> 00:20:34.681
FEELINGS OF. UH. FONDNESS.

538
00:20:34.750 --> 00:20:35.782
AND MORE...

539
00:20:35.851 --> 00:20:37.167
[Laughs nervously]

540
00:20:37.236 --> 00:20:39.636
YOU KNOW WHAT I
MEAN. DON'T YOU. BOY?

541
00:20:39.705 --> 00:20:40.938
NO.

542
00:20:41.006 --> 00:20:42.356
[Sighing]

543
00:20:42.424 --> 00:20:43.523
WELL. UH...

544
00:20:43.592 --> 00:20:44.808
[High-pitched wheeze]

545
00:20:44.860 --> 00:20:46.571
THAT'S A HELL OF A WEIRD SOUND.

546
00:20:46.595 --> 00:20:48.511
I NEVER MADE THAT BEFORE.

547
00:20:48.580 --> 00:20:50.029
UH. I...

548
00:20:50.699 --> 00:20:51.699
YOU...

549
00:20:51.767 --> 00:20:52.999
UH...

550
00:20:53.068 --> 00:20:54.285
FAMILY.

551
00:20:56.638 --> 00:20:59.356
YOU'RE NOT MAKING
THIS EASY ON ME. BOY.

552
00:20:59.425 --> 00:21:00.524
[Sighs]

553
00:21:00.593 --> 00:21:01.992
OK.

554
00:21:02.060 --> 00:21:04.406
I LOVE YOU NO MATTER
WHAT YOU DO. THERE! WHEW!

555
00:21:04.430 --> 00:21:06.758
LET'S GO GET SOMETHING TO EAT!

556
00:21:06.782 --> 00:21:08.648
I'M NOT...

557
00:21:08.718 --> 00:21:11.084
JUST A BIG
DISAPPOINTMENT TO YOU?

558
00:21:11.153 --> 00:21:12.636
DISAPPOINTMENT?

559
00:21:12.704 --> 00:21:14.705
NO. YOU MAKE ME PROUD.

560
00:21:14.774 --> 00:21:16.084
I'VE BEEN DISAPPOINTED

561
00:21:16.108 --> 00:21:18.353
BY JUST ABOUT EVERYTHING
ELSE IN THIS TOWN.

562
00:21:18.377 --> 00:21:20.422
BUT YOU? NOT ONCE.

563
00:21:20.446 --> 00:21:22.963
DAMN IT. YOU'RE MY BOY.

564
00:21:23.032 --> 00:21:25.109
YOU KNOW BETTER THAN THAT.

565
00:21:25.133 --> 00:21:26.600
[Giggling]

566
00:21:26.669 --> 00:21:28.814
[Social worker] HE PUNCHED
HIM! I KNEW IT! I TOLD THEM!

567
00:21:28.838 --> 00:21:29.953
D-DID YOU SEE THAT?

568
00:21:30.022 --> 00:21:31.755
SEE WHAT. TWIG BOY?

569
00:21:31.824 --> 00:21:33.156
[Sighs] NEVER MIND.

569
00:21:34.305 --> 00:22:34.802
